//|------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
//| Syntax                                                                       |
//|------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
//|button Button1 | text 250 250 100 25 145 85 55                                |
//|          ^    |   ^    ^  ^   ^  ^   ^  ^  ^                                 |
//|          N    |  Text  X  Y   W  H   R  G  B                                 |
//| Name,         | Text, X position, Y position, Width, height Red, Green, Blue |
//|---------------|--------------------------------------------------------------|
//| Necessary     |  Optional                                                    |
//|------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
//|Examples:                                                                     |
//|------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
//|button btn Press\_Me 250 50 100 45 255 0 0                                    |
//|button helpBtn help                                                           |
//|------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
//| Calling the Values:                                                          |
//|------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
//|button:name:value                                                             |
//|              ^                                                               |
//|   value (eg. x, y, width, height, r, g, b)                                   |
//|------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
//| Examle:                                                                      |
//|------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
//|button:btn:x                                                                  |
//|------------------------------------------------------------------------------|

// Btn
button Btn Press\_Me! 100 330 335 25 0 255 0
buttonClick Btn ~/Scripts/Woohoo.ezcode

// Words
button Words Random\_Word 100 365 335 25 120 120 255
buttonClick Words ~/Scripts/RandomWord.ezcode

// Quit
button Quit Quit 110 400 315 25 255 0 0
buttonClick Quit ~/Scripts/Quit.ezcode